<a href="javascript:;" class="show-all" id="showMore">
<em>展开全文</em>
</a>
</section>
</div>
<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p class="ql-align-center">四岁红遍语文课本，长大以后他却颠覆了所有人的想象 </p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201030/020a92f1934447d5bc140a2d27133670.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">诺贝尔</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">从小<strong>体弱多病</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">上学都是上一休四</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201030/6767c8ab023d436e887b3ede59333e9f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这并不妨碍他是班里</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">成绩优异的好学生</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201030/687b43c4a93e435e83679e390a9ff2cb.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">成绩优异的小孩</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">想法总是<strong>不同于常人</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">当别的小朋友在为是成为</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">科学家还是宇航员烦恼时</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">诺贝尔瞅着自家那个</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">整天捣鼓炸药的老爹</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">问出了这样一个问题</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201030/548ece54f90f429cb6726618a4eb4ab4.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">老爹语重心长回答道</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201030/6f76342363414ff2b3aa98b819bb8597.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">听完这段话</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">小小的诺贝尔</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有了个大大的梦想</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">他决定</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">要做出世界上<strong>最牛逼的炸药</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201030/c0fdb5ddbb3544aaa1c2be7eb6b3e1e6.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">其实早在<strong>1847年</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就有个意大利人<strong>索伯雷罗</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">发现了一种很牛逼炸药</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>硝化甘油</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">虽说威力强是真的强</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">但缺点也是很致命</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">——<strong>极其不稳定</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">生产、运输、使用过程中</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>随·时·可·能·爆·炸</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">所以</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">硝化甘油并没有被大量运用起来</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201030/f1b6c1e1578f4bdbb3cb317b6725a9a9.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">诺贝尔想法就很不一样了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">既然这么危险</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那让它变安全不就好了吗</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这样就能造福各位开矿工</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">让挖矿<strong>变得更快乐</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">然后</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">他用包括自个儿老弟在内的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">5条人命验证了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">硝化甘油是真的很易爆</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201030/166229da311a477797ee2448d828396f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这一炸</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">诺贝尔本人倒不是太慌</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">毕竟</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">疯狂的科学家们都深知一个道理</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">化学就是爆炸</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">所以继续无视死亡威胁</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在死亡实验边缘<strong>反复试探</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201030/d5a2ff6431d14332ab260b3373f807b3.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">对于普通吃瓜群众来说</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这事儿可就大了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">虽然这次炸的是你家</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">但谁能保证</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">下次会不会炸到我们家</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">所以告去政府那边</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>禁止诺贝尔继续搞这种危险研究</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201030/907c5e0edf6b4c5ea95f4fd05ba77241.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">没办法</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">地上不给搞</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那就<strong>下海</strong>搞吧</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">于是</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">诺贝尔自个儿搞了搜船</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在船上继续研究硝化甘油</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201030/03f8509182ec4ff9b5fde11fe9874d18.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">最后</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">船没沉 <strong>诺贝尔成了</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201030/bc6d0e3eccf0464bb0c50821ab657a18.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">硝化甘油炸药</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">是易燃易爆危险品这事儿</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">已经深深<strong>刻在群众的脑瓜子里</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">空口说安全没用</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">实践才能出真知</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">于是诺贝尔在隔壁山头</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">把炸药火烤</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还从高处丢下去</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>都没有爆炸</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">只有用雷管引爆才会真的爆炸</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">消除了大家的顾虑</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">从此</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">开始躺着都能赚的人生</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201030/b60fa58ca8044903923da02e8ea09893.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">当诺贝尔的事业走向光明时</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">爱情却一路黑到了底</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">倒不是因为沉迷工作无心恋爱</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而是恋爱运这东西</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">和他实在是无缘</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201030/57514f44ed304133b4657671ad4e9883.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">说起诺贝尔的初恋</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">倒是挺不错</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">两人<strong>互相欣赏</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">没什么小三出轨的烂俗剧情</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">但</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">却有着青春恋爱剧的狗血套路</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那就是</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在你侬我侬都还没过的热恋期</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">姑娘突然就<strong>肺结核死了</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201030/6882a0d2021e474a988da9fbaabc0116.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">第二次恋爱</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">是等到诺贝尔四十三岁</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">也就是有钱之后</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">实验忙没空管日常生活</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">于是招聘了个女秘书兼管家</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">然后</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就是你想的那样</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">诺贝尔爱上了女管家</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201030/d7849c057f5947819d254ce9950ab086.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">女管家却爱着奥地利的男爵</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">虽然</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">女管家和男爵经常<strong>闹别扭</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">诺贝尔常年在隔壁旁边<strong>劝分</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">但你们也知道的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这类人你越是劝分</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">他们反而感情更好</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">最终</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">女管家选择了男爵</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">趁着诺贝尔出差回去见男爵然后<strong>闪婚</strong>了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201030/f25e66785f9e4ee4b6056b912c0b00ff.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">第三次恋爱</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在女管家去闪婚后不久</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">诺贝尔也去奥地利散心</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">结识了一个美丽的卖花女郎</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">两人<strong>一拍即合</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">从此诺贝尔光荣地成为了一个</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>移动取款机</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">惨的不止是被当成取款机</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而是取你的款去怀别人的娃</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">甚至要取更多的钱支持她养娃</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201030/89eeb07402234589b221e11dd4d461d8.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">舔狗真的强</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">诺贝尔还真持续打钱</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">企图通过打钱挽回她的心</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一打就是好几年</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">等娃都三岁了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">诺贝尔抱着希望以及勇气</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">前去看望她</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">结果对方依旧把他当成取款机</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">然后和别人结婚了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201030/28f3a132cf424efda22a6cc42baaa922.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">晚年的诺贝尔不仅想不通</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">为什么自己这辈子恋爱运这么差</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">更想不到</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">为什么医生在自己药方上</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">开了个<strong>“炸药”</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201030/b352c812fdaa4aa5bf82a73be5f75c6b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201030/9375ee1bc4ce4e59af8fea42898da437.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">其实在诺贝尔建厂搞炸药后</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">厂里的工人们就出现了一种情况</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">上班时候头痛+发烫</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">可到了周末</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">情况就会变好</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201030/8ea6e894ecc1423fadc4668455de4903.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">药理学家们一听</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>兴趣就来了</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">立刻关注到这事儿</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">然后发现是硝化甘油搞的事</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">硝化甘油有<strong>扩张血管</strong>的功效</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">工人们<strong>天天在厂里和硝化甘油作伴</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">导致脑部血管扩张</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">才引发头痛发烫这些问题</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">于是硝化甘油便慢慢被研发成了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一种<strong>缓解心脏病的药</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201030/1b30588d37394dc59b4227382bda8c84.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">晚年的诺贝尔</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">正好就有<strong>心绞痛的问题</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">于是医生对症下药</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">给他开了硝化甘油缓解</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不过都被诺贝尔<strong>拒绝了</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201030/af47ca09c51d479f8416a62bb2daf10a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">结果在<strong>1998年</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">也就是</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">诺贝尔因心脏病去世102年后</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">三位科学家</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">凭借对硝化甘油治疗心脏病的研究</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">获得了<strong>诺贝尔医学奖</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而诺贝尔奖的出现</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">也与硝化甘油密不可分</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">倒不是因为卖硝化甘油</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">赚了太多钱没地儿花</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">随便搞个奖让大家崇拜崇拜</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">相反</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有一种赎罪的意味</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201030/1bd7e02236ec4327b0aef51683ffa5be.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">研究硝化甘油炸药的初衷</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">是为了让采矿和修路工人更轻松</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">结果却被大量用于战争中</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">成为杀人武器</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">导致许多无辜生命的死亡</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">所以诺贝尔最终<strong>将自己的钱用做基金</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">授予全世界对人类作出重大贡献的人</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201030/9c7d0b3f0eda48e78480b874124114e6.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">诺贝尔不知道</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在这个世界上</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还有个和自己很相似的人</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">他是一位医生</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">因看战场中伤亡太多被深深刺痛</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">于是决定<strong>弃医从理</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">发明一种保护士兵的武器</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201030/d95aac7a77d54715be0c28088076006b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这个武器依靠<strong>凶勐的火力</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">让一个士兵替代一个连的兵力</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">减少了战场上士兵的人数</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">以达到减少战争伤亡的目的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这个医生的名字叫</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>理查·乔登·加特林</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">至于他发明了什么</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不用朕多说了吧</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201030/b1f374bed1ef42a0905dd18465a3d0da.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">本文系【朕说】原创内容</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">未经账号授权，禁止随意转载</p>